## ComicModel
```dart
class ComicModel {
  String id;
  String title;
  String plot;
  ComicStyle style; // Enum: cyberpunk, fantasy, etc.
  int panelCount; // 2-4 panels
  List<String> imageUrls; // Generated comic images
  
  // Constructor and methods should be simple (no freezed)
}

enum ComicStyle {
  cyberpunk,    // 赛博朋克
  fantasy,      // 奇幻
  sciFi,        // 科幻
  modern,       // 现代
  other         // 其他
}
```

Remember to keep models simple and avoid complex patterns like freezed or part syntax.
